metadata.description: He came from Spain, he ain't no bird or plane!  It's Ultracat!  With his ultra-speed, ultra-strength and ultra-cuteness, the world's feistiest feline conquers all criminals, from minor burglars to super-villains to that annoying evildoer pug across the hall!  Just don't ask him to go out in the rain or pass up a nap...
metadata.name: Ultracat
